    "This may enhance the lives and food security of smallholder farmers (Beesigamukama et al., 2022).",
    "Using BSFL frass as a value-added product has been added profitable for BSFL farming than using just the net income from BSFL animal feed.",
    "Compost-like qualities can be seen in BSFL frass (Bortolini et al., 2020).",
    "According to several studies (Attiogbe et al., 2019; Bortolini et al., 2020; Gao et al., 2019; Sarpong et al., 2019), the quick composting of organic waste by BSFL produced compacted BSFL frass with high macronutrients (NPK), micronutrients, and organic material contents that are immediately usable for agricultural application.",
    "In contrast to BSF farming alone, using BSFL frass fertiliser increased farmers' net income by 5-15 times, according to a study by Beesigamukama et al. (2020a)."
